revision.text: ==English== ===Etymology=== Coined by {{w|John Stenhouse}} from {{suffix|en|{{ll|mul|Xanthoxylum}}|ene|t1=syn. of ''[[Zanthoxylum]]''}}. ===Noun=== {{en-noun|-}} # {{lb|en|archaic|chemistry}} A [[terpene]] extracted from the [[seed]]s of the {{vern|Japanese prickly ash}} ({{taxlink|Zanthoxylum pipertium|species|ver=200607}}).
